text:
My favorite thing in the world is when @FedEx doesn't knock on the door and just leaves a door tag. 

Bonus points for routing the package through Rocklin to make it that much harder to get to!

@kylebuis Hi, my name is Bobby. I am sorry for any issues you have experienced with your delivery. Would you like me to check on your shipment for you? Please DM your name, address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r
@FedExHelp I already did the 50-ish mile drive to get it.
@kylebuis I am glad you received your delivery. Have a great evening! - Bobby
